    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-teal-50 border-[3px] border-emerald-300 p-8 md:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8 tracking-tight">MY EXPERIENCE</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">Dr. Michael Torres, Portland family physician. 17 years practice. <span class="font-black text-emerald-600">Problem:</span> website looked like 2005 basic template. <span class="font-black text-emerald-600">Fix:</span> brutal redesign with credibility focus. <span class="font-black text-emerald-600">Result:</span> 287% more new patient appointments in 90 days.</p>

