        </div>

        <div class="border-l-[3px] border-cyan-500 pl-6 py-5 bg-cyan-50/50 rounded-r mb-6">
          <p class="text-sm font-black text-cyan-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">THE FIX: WEBFLOW HIPAA-COMPLIANT SITE WITH CREDIBILITY FOCUS</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Dr. Torres chose Webflow for custom HIPAA disclaimers and compliance control. Built: brutal hero with "Board Certified MD, 17 Years Experience" badge, credentials prominently displayed (MD, ABFM, OHSU Medical School), insurance accepted list visible (Blue Cross, Aetna, Cigna, Medicare, Regence), online appointment request form with HIPAA-compliant data handling, patient reviews section (4.8/5 from 400+ patients), new patient information downloadable, health blog with preventive care tips, telehealth option prominently, mobile-optimized appointment booking. HIPAA compliance: custom disclaimers on data collection, BAA with scheduling platform. Investment: $3,600 (design + legal review + 6 months hosting). Launch: 3 days.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-[3px] border-emerald-500 pl-6 py-5 bg-emerald-50/50 rounded-r mb-6">
          <p class="text-sm font-black text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">THE AFTER (90 DAYS): 162 NEW PATIENTS/MONTH, $243,000 REVENUE, 193% INCREASE</p>
