          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-gray-900">Days 1-30:</strong> Webflow site launched (March 8). Credentials prominent immediately ("Board Certified MD, 17 Years"). Week 1: new patient inquiries increased 127% (42 ‚Üí 95). Patients cite "qualified doctor" as #1 booking reason. Week 2: added insurance accepted list prominently (March 15). Qualified calls increased 67% (patients know they can afford). Week 3: added online appointment request form with HIPAA-compliant data handling (March 22). 73% of patients book online without calling. Week 4: added patient reviews section (March 29). 4.8/5 rating visible. Qualified inquiries increased 53%. Month 1 total: 108 new patients, $108,000 revenue.<br/><br/><strong class="text-gray-900">Days 31-60:</strong> Health blog launched with preventive care content (April 12). 28 organic patients/month from educational content (flu prevention, chronic disease management). Added telehealth option prominently (April 19). Busy professional inquiries increased 43% (convenience). New patient forms downloadable (April 26). Patient preparation improved, no-show rate dropped 40%. Integrated click-to-call buttons for mobile (May 3). Mobile booking increased 61%. Month 2 total: 127 new patients, $152,000 revenue.<br/><br/><strong class="text-gray-900">Days 61-90:</strong> Health blog reached 50+ articles (May 17). Organic traffic: 73 patients/month from search (up from 28). Patient reviews hit 500+ testimonials (May 24). Social proof: trust increased 67%. Enhanced mobile experience with one-touch booking (June 2). Mobile bookings hit 81% (was 57%). Added "Same-Day Appointments Available" for urgent cases (June 14). Urgent care inquiries increased 127%. Month 3 total: 162 new patients, $243,000 revenue. 90-day total: $243,000 vs $126,000 previous quarter = 93% increase. Investment: $3,600. ROI: 6,650% in 90 days.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <p class="text-xs font-black text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">THE 90-DAY BREAKDOWN IN NUMBERS</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
            <div>
              <p class="text-3xl font-black text-emerald-600">42‚Üí162</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 mt-1">New patients/mo</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-3xl font-black text-emerald-600">$126K‚Üí$243K</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 mt-1">Quarterly revenue</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-3xl font-black text-emerald-600">6,650%</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 mt-1">ROI</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
